OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780989354
OL,3,CHealth officials confirm university
OL,4,Cmeningitis case
OL,6,FHealth officials have confirmed a case
OL,7,Fof meningitis at the University of
OL,8,FSurrey.
OL,10,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,11,Fsaid it was in touch with close
OL,12,Fcontacts of the case and arranging
OL,13,Fvaccination and preventative
OL,14,Fantibiotic appointments.
OL,16,FIt added there is no evidence that it
OL,17,Fis linked to any previous cases or
OL,18,Foutbreaks, and that the risk to the
OL,19,Fpublic remains low.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
