CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780989354
OL,3,CHealth officials confirm university
OL,4,Cmeningitis case
OL,6,FThe agency added it is sharing advice
OL,7,Fwith students to raise awareness
OL,8,Faround signs and symptoms of the
OL,9,Fdisease.
OL,11,FJaime Morgan, Principal Health
OL,12,FProtection Lead at UKHSA South East
OL,13,Fsaid: "We understand that news of
OL,14,Fmeningococcal infection can be
OL,15,Fconcerning.
OL,17,F"However meningococcal meningitis
OL,18,Frequires very close contact to spread
OL,19,Fand large outbreaks as we saw in Kent
OL,20,Frecently, are thankfully rare.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
